BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:AB8q8dyE7PIEm5d_QYBrB
SUMMARY:World Class Music Presents: Dobet Gnahore
DTSTAMP:20260306T011840Z
DTSTART:20260405T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:While Africa has blessed the world with many recognized female 
	artists\, Dobet Gnahoré has proven herself to be a truly special talent an
	d her latest album Zouzou demonstrates that she is at her creative prime. 
	Known for her ability to infuse her music with soul-stirring energy and me
	ssage-driven lyrics\, Gnahoré showcases her incredible range as an artist 
	in this new collection of songs. Through a combination of traditional and 
	contemporary influences\, she crafts a unique sound that is both distinct 
	and accessible to audiences worldwide. The album features an array of stan
	dout tracks that explore themes such as resilience\, unity\, and the power
	 of community. Gnahoré’s dynamic vocal performance and skilled musicianshi
	p shine throughout the album\, making Zouzou an unforgettable journey for 
	listeners. Buy Tickets Here.\n\nhttps://rainierartscenter.org/events/world
	-class-music-presents-dobet-gnahore/
URL:https://rainierartscenter.org/events/world-class-music-presents-dobet-g
	nahore/
LOCATION:Auditorium\, Rainier Arts Center\, 3515 S Alaska St\, Seattle\, WA
	 98118
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H30M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:yBWXDorx1QCcHGsGvXdvf
SUMMARY:Off Book Productions Presents: James and the Giant Peach
DTSTAMP:20260306T011840Z
DTSTART:20260316T010000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a juicy adventure bursting with imagination! James 
	and the Giant Peach Jr. brings Roald Dahl’s beloved story to life in a del
	ightful\, high-energy musical for all ages. Follow young James as he escap
	es a dreary life and embarks on an unforgettable journey across the ocean 
	inside a giant peach—alongside a crew of quirky\, lovable insect friends. 
	Packed with catchy songs\, colorful characters\, and plenty of heart\, thi
	s fun-filled production is a sweet treat the whole family will love. Buy T
	ickets\n\nhttps://rainierartscenter.org/events/off-book-productions-presen
	ts-james-and-the-giant-peach-4/
URL:https://rainierartscenter.org/events/off-book-productions-presents-jame
	s-and-the-giant-peach-4/
LOCATION:Auditorium\, Rainier Arts Center\, 3515 S Alaska St\, Seattle\, WA
	 98118
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
